  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they marched them away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After they went, we had no Germans, nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were all free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were by ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was no Russians, no Germans, no nothing-- no electricity, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "First thing we all did is go into the storeroom and got bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we-- I remember holding my bread under my, whatever I was wearing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I had bread, bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Wherever I-- wherever you touched me, I had bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was completely insulated well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the second thing we did is go into the storerooms and got ourselves dressed warmly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So if you see on those pictures all of us wearing babushkas and nice clothes, it's because we went to the storerooms, and we got ourselves dressed after the Germans left.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because this is not the kind of clothes we were liberated-- I mean, these are not the kind of clothes that we were in the camp with.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This-- this was heaven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We dressed ourselves.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I remember having this particular cute story is that I wanted to have boots.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I wanted to have boots, and I couldn't find boots that were matching.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they had to be boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I found one boot in-- in like a luggage color, a deep luggage color, like a brownish luggage color.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was brownish leather with-- with that caca-color [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] felt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I couldn't find the mate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That fit me a little better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't find a mate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I finally was so frustrated-- and they-- all the kids, they wanted to leave-- that I-- I found another boot, and it was black leather with white felt.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Close enough.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had-- [LAUGHS] and it was much bigger.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
